ZH: 她辛勤工作了一整天。
EN: She worked hard all day.

ZH: 这个农民一年四季都在辛勤耕种。
EN: This farmer works hard in all seasons.

ZH: 我们要向辛勤努力的教师们致敬。
EN: We salute the hard-working teachers.

ZH: 辛勤劳动是实现梦想的基石。
EN: Hard work is the foundation of achieving dreams.

ZH: 他通过辛勤努力，成功地获得了晋升。
EN: Through diligent efforts, he successfully got promoted.

ZH: 学生们为了考试而辛勤学习。
EN: Students study hard for exams.

ZH: 这家工厂的员工都是辛勤工作的。
EN: The employees in this factory all work hard.

ZH: 辛勤种植，收获丰硕。
EN: Hard cultivation leads to bountiful harvests.

ZH: 他以辛勤的工作态度取得了巨大的进步。
EN: He made great progress with his diligent work attitude.

ZH: 辛勤耕耘的果实将会甜美可口。
EN: The fruits of hard labor will be sweet and delicious.

ZH: 他辛勤地工作以养活一家人。
EN: He works hard to support his family.

ZH: 辛勤是成功的必备条件之一。
EN: Hard work is one of the essential conditions for success.

ZH: 他通过辛勤锻炼，获得了出色的身体素质。
EN: He achieved outstanding physical fitness through diligent exercise.

ZH: 这个项目得以成功完成，要归功于所有辛勤付出的工人。
EN: The successful completion of this project is thanks to all the hardworking workers.

ZH: 在寒冷的冬天里，他们依然辛勤地工作。
EN: They still work hard in the cold winter.

ZH: 辛勤的汗水浇灌着幸福的花朵。
EN: The flowers of happiness are watered by the sweat of hard work.

ZH: 没有辛勤的付出，就不会有美好的未来。
EN: Without diligent effort, there will be no bright future.

ZH: 她靠着辛勤工作攒下了一笔不错的积蓄。
EN: She saved a decent amount of money through hard work.

ZH: 长期辛勤的努力最终将会取得回报。
EN: Long-term diligent efforts will eventually pay off.

ZH: 辛勤工作是实现个人价值的重要途径之一。
EN: Hard work is one of the important ways to achieve personal value.
